{"tid":910711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大陸臭蟹】呢排都係咪撚食大閘蟹 原來好多走私蟹","createTime":"2018-11-21T11:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T12:06:51.000Z","uid":101994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6a9cdfcebd10c1c5ca15b252f6faf4071c0131","tid":910711,"uid":101994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:16:50.000Z","msg":"自9月踏入蟹季以來，內地至今尚未就大閘蟹供港發出批文，本港亦只有少量商舖以迂迴的方式，將自內地出口至其他國家的大閘蟹，運到香港出售，不過，坊間仍有人以「自己方法」，將大閘蟹自深圳經羅湖口岸，運抵香港。《香港01》接獲投訴，近日有「水貨兵團」疑似由羅湖走私大閘蟹到粉嶺港鐵站散貨，記者連日來追訪，直擊水貨客手持大量「蟹貨」過關，猶如「攞正牌」通行無阻，各人更肆無忌憚高談濶談走私過程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fHhpX1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHhpX1c.png&h=a623c7ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RaTsVNT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRaTsVNT.png&h=16a8360a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rmPjMUz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrmPjMUz.png&h=8aece0cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文太撚長，淨係擺引言出嚟，有興趣自己入去睇<br />\n咁搞法，叫我點食大閘蟹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆街大陸狗、香港走私狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/260845/%E8%B5%B0%E7%A7%81%E5%A4%A7%E9%96%98%E8%9F%B9-%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BE%9B%E6%B8%AF%E6%89%B9%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AA%E5%87%BA-%E5%A4%A7%E9%96%98%E8%9F%B9%E8%B5%B0%E7%A7%81%E5%88%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%A8%E7%A8%8B%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A\" data-sr-url